    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Terminology: </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="7" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:189px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" style="text-align:right;">Ball-Joint : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> makes a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text> in a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Connecting-Part</text> coincident with a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text> in a different <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">You must add <text styleclass="VariableName-small">2 x </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joints</text> to add a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> to each end of a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Connecting-Part </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">:</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:15px; font-family:Symbol; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:15px;"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">1 x </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint </text>between <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Points</text> in different <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> that are in the active <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor</text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:15px; font-family:Symbol; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:15px;"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">1 x </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint </text>between <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Points</text> in different <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> that are in different <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editors</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:189px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Spherical-Joint : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The kinematic and equivalent term for a <text styleclass="Element">Ball-Joint</text>. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:189px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2" style="text-align:right;">Kinematics-Tree : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Dyads R-S-S, P-S-S</text> - the joints in a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">dyad</text> use the letter <text styleclass="VariableName-small">S</text> for a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text>. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Derived Names: </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:189px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Connecting-Part : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> with a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> at its <text styleclass="Popup Box2">start-Point</text> and at its <text styleclass="Popup Box2">end-Point</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:189px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Part that is Completely-Free :</para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> with 3 degrees-of-freedom (no joints).</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:189px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Part that is Free : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> with 1 or 2 degrees-of-freedom. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also:<text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-BallJoint">Ball-Joint dialog</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="" anchor="EditConnecting-Part">Connecting Part Length and Diameter</link>.</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Ball-Joint-Configurations">Ball-Joint configurations</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
